Localization.Name: DMC
Localization.Description: Still renowned for their denim, DMC (Denim Manufacture Corporation) has become so much more. From durable outerwear to rugged fashion, DMC knows that feeling good is just as important as looking good.

Localization.Name: Greenwater Shirt Olive
Localization.Description: The Greenwater is a long-sleeved shirt tailor-made to be worn underneath most standard sets of armor. Crafted with a durable mix of natural and synthetic fibers, it stands up to daily wear and tear without sacrificing comfort.
